      "content": {
        "title": "Limb Length Discrepancy and Angular Deformity — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Leg length inequality and coronal or sagittal angular deformities from congenital, developmental, or post-traumatic causes.",
        "summary": "Moseley charting predicts growth remaining. Guided growth for angular correction; epiphysiodesis or lengthening for LLD."
